{"word":"G5455 - φωνέω - phōnéō - fo-neh'-o - Call","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phōnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fo-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Call</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழை, கூவு, கூப்பிடு, சத்தமிடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to sound, emit a sound, to speak"},{"paragraph":"2. to call, to invite"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5456 - φωνή - phōnḗ - fo-nay'/5456\">G5456</a>; to emit a <i>sound</i> (animal, human or instrumental); by implication to <i>address</i> in words or by name, also in imitation: - call (for), crow, cry.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2019/2019\">G2019</a>, <a href=\"#/G4856/4856\">G4856</a>, <a href=\"#/G4857/4857\">G4857</a>, <a href=\"#/G4858/4858\">G4858</a>, <a href=\"#/G4859/4859\">G4859</a>, <a href=\"#/G5455/5455\">G5455</a>, <a href=\"#/G5456/5456\">G5456</a>"}]}